summary: This mod adds required to skill level for armors and weapons
descriptionHtml:
[size=3]This mod adds required to skill level for armors and weapons. [/size]
[size=3]If your skill is low then you will not be able to use the armor/weapon.[/size]
Requirements for skills you can see in the table.
[size=3]Mod was designed for the game with the [/size][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/19281/]requiem[/url][size=3]. But you can use it with vanilla game.[/size]
[size=4]
[/size][size=4]Required:[/size]
[list]
[*][size=3]Skyrim[/size]
[*][size=3]Dragonborn[/size]
[*][size=3]Dawnguard[/size]
[*][size=3]USLEP[/size]
[*][size=3]SKSE[/size]
[/list][size=3]

[/size][size=4]Compatibility:[/size]
[size=3]This mod will work with any mods to add the weapon/armor, if author of mod used standard keywords.

Example:

[youtube]6WmI8FmIW_E[/youtube][/size]
author: Dimitry
